atar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146", "stars": 3518, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 692431, "username": "wayfarer", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wayfarer", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0f99/cf86/692431_mini.png?m=1753428172", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0f99/cf86/692431_normal.png?m=1753428172", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0f99/cf86/692431_large.png?m=1753428172", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0f99/cf86/692431_xlarge.png?m=1753428172", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0f99/cf86/692431_xxlarge.png?m=1753428172", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0f99/cf86/692431_xxxlarge.png?m=1753428172", "created": 1716456744, "last_modified": 1753428172, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Awes0me", "last_touched": 1760200282, "title": "工时太短，被领导约谈了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1164476", "created": 1760168624, "deleted": 0, "content": "刚刚被领导叫去谈话了，说我上个月平均工时全部门倒数第一。\r\n我是上个月刚入入职的，工作量不多，所以基本是到点就走。\r\n我说我有没迟到没早退，该做的工作都做完了，在这耗着也没意义。\r\n领导的意思是，工时会影响绩效，如果没啥急事，下班后尽量多待一会，哪怕是摸会鱼。\r\n我刚问了一下旁边的同事，他说大部分同事都是七点之后才走。\r\n\r\n有点难评。", "content_rendered": "<p>刚刚被领导叫去谈话了，说我上个月平均工时全部门倒数第一。\n我是上个月刚入入职的，工作量不多，所以基本是到点就走。\n我说我有没迟到没早退，该做的工作都做完了，在这耗着也没意义。\n领导的意思是，工时会影响绩效，如果没啥急事，下班后尽量多待一会，哪怕是摸会鱼。\n我刚问了一下旁边的同事，他说大部分同事都是七点之后才走。</p>\n<p>有点难评。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1760168624, "replies": 52, "id": 1164476}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 234257, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.co